  "solution": {
    "answer": "$H_0(\\mathbb{R}P^2) \\cong \\mathbb{Z},\\quad H_1(\\mathbb{R}P^2) \\cong \\mathbb{Z}/2,\\quad H_n(\\mathbb{R}P^2) = 0 \\text{ for } n \\geq 2.$",
    "steps": [
      "CW structure: one 0-cell $v$, one 1-cell $a$, one 2-cell $e$ attached by the degree-2 map $a^2$.",
      "Chain complex: $0 \\to \\mathbb{Z} \\xrightarrow{d_2} \\mathbb{Z} \\xrightarrow{d_1} \\mathbb{Z} \\to 0$.",
      "$d_1(a) = v - v = 0$; $d_2(e) = 2\\cdot a$ (the attaching map winds around the 1-skeleton twice).",
      "$H_2 = \\ker(d_2) = \\ker(\\times 2: \\mathbb{Z} \\to \\mathbb{Z}) = 0$ (multiplication by 2 is injective).",
      "$H_1 = \\ker(d_1)/\\operatorname{im}(d_2) = \\mathbb{Z}/2\\mathbb{Z} \\cong \\mathbb{Z}/2$.",
      "$H_0 = \\mathbb{Z}$. $\\mathbb{R}P^2$ is non-orientable, consistent with $H_2 = 0$."
    ]
  },
